- `src/server.ts` — `Bun.serve()` with routing for `/fizzbuzz/:n`, `/fizzbuzz?from=&to=`, `/health`, and 404s
- `tests/fizzbuzz.test.ts` — 6 unit test cases for core function
- `tests/server.test.ts` — 18 integration tests for HTTP layer
- `package.json`, `tsconfig.json` — project config

**Endpoints:**
- `GET /fizzbuzz/:n` — single fizzbuzz result
- `GET /fizzbuzz?from=1&to=100` — range (max 1000)
- `GET /health` — health check
- Everything else → 404

